{"tid":905904,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Huh] 盜墓者羅拉:暗影 走火入魔主線一氣呵成版 中文字幕","createTime":"2018-11-17T13:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T17:58:34.000Z","uid":105546,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d374d834dd6c6b23efcf4eb0fc56127853effab6","tid":905904,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"雖然係遲左啲,但有興趣或者未睇過嘅巴絲如果只想睇主線同殺下人嘅可以click入去睇下<br />\n走火入魔同叢林之王(第二難度)嘅分別只係無本能同自動存檔 <br />\n本來我諗住挑戰一命爆機但去到中後期唔小心死左兩次 所以我將重打之後嘅片合成<br />\n所以得番一氣呵成版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望巴絲見諒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未來幾日我會出多條古墓合集 但我唔會刷新po 蹲求各位subscribe我之後留意下  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KInIeZVeRAs&amp;t=7195s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKInIeZVeRAs%26t%3D7195s&d=5cca5s3p9ov1qVPWD0M9HV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=33863833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KInIeZVeRAs&amp;t=7195s</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟會時不時推下個po 不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cfff99a043533074ca287d8eee4c9f25b1c3d6","tid":905904,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"3a970feb31096795c81cb8bf100797dd56dde031","tid":905904,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d58c7a2e90723e59a943a0f0f269248eb254bd49","tid":905904,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"22b59225e703d97c2b41dce84ac529c4ca682d01","tid":905904,"uid":105546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"07ecd0e8a6925